<P>
 Procter & Gamble Likely to Get OK to Buy German Firm: The European Commission 
is expected to clear plans by Procter & Gamble Co. to buy hygiene products firm 
VP-Schickedanz following changes in the deal that make it compatible with 
competition rules. Competition Commissioner Karel Van Miert recommended to his 
