Management $1,100 2 Julian Robertson Tiger Management 500 3 Michael Steinhardt 
Steinhardt Management 474 4 Stanley Druckenmiller Soros Fund Management 210 5 
Bruce Kovner Caxton Corp. 200 6 Paul Kazarian Japonica Partners 148 7 Alfred 
Lerner Private Investor 99.3 8 Mark Strome Strome Susskind 90 9 Leon Cooperman 
Omega Advisors 70-85 10 Victor Posner & family private investor 60  
</P>
