<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 16, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Long Beach; Part J; Page 10; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
